oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Multiple recording takes of Just Moved in / Our Love Won't Stop
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Recording is of a number of recording takes of two songs: "Just Moved in" and "Our Love Won't Stop." The recording is done by an unidentified group.
